  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    public class Course
extends Activity
    Course Class: Designed to hold the properties of a course and be able to be manipulated through getters/setters A subclass of Activity as to be incorporated into a schedule through the user using WolfScheduler getShortDisplayArray and getLongDisplayArray are used to output contents of the course for the client to view isDuplicate compares 2 courses to see if they're the same
    Author:
    yash
